tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE training_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_id INT,
  model_id INT,
  accuracy FLOAT,
  training_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (data_id) REFERENCES preprocessing_data(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES machine_learning_model(id)
);

CREATE TABLE evaluation_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_id INT,
  model_id INT,
  evaluation_metric VARCHAR,
  evaluation_result VARCHAR,
  evaluation_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (data_id) REFERENCES preprocessing_data(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES machine_learning_model(id)
);
